922
01:01:57,213 --> 01:01:58,506
You son of a bitch!

923
01:01:58,589 --> 01:01:59,841
[dramatic music playing]

924
01:02:01,426 --> 01:02:02,593
[man 1 groans]

925
01:02:06,264 --> 01:02:07,640
[music fades]

926
01:02:07,724 --> 01:02:09,517
